Properties.Name: Get All Star Group Leaders and Groups

Properties.Value:
{% sql %}SELECT CONCAT (
        lgm.PersonId
        , '|'
        , string_agg(g.Id, ';')
        ) AS PersonId
FROM GroupMember gm
INNER JOIN [Group] g
    ON g.Id = gm.GroupId
INNER JOIN GroupMember lgm
    ON lgm.GroupId = g.Id
INNER JOIN GroupTypeRole gtr
    ON lgm.GroupRoleId = gtr.Id
WHERE g.GroupTypeId IN (112, 113)
    AND gm.PersonId = {{ Workflow | Attribute:'Person','Id' }}
    AND gm.GroupMemberStatus <> 0
    AND gm.IsArchived <> 1
    AND lgm.GroupMemberStatus <> 0
    AND lgm.IsArchived <> 1
    AND gtr.Id IN (215, 219)
    AND g.IsActive = 1
    AND g.IsArchived <> 1
GROUP BY lgm.PersonId{% endsql %}
{{ results | Map:'PersonId' | Join:',' }}
